Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:01.50,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\pos(520,250)}川島亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:36.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,270)\fs30}真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------正文------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長假也只剩下今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家準備如何度過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒得都快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  都怪劣等狗太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見不到北村也不是我的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為連休期間社團活動和學生會的事會很忙  我不是說了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法解決才是狗的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就算見到了也沒辦法好好說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下地獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被潑到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  拿什麼擦的東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你胡扯才會這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  總之先用這個擦下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們準備在泰泰睡覺的時候兩個人吃蛋包飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的份包好了保鮮膜放在冰箱裏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好寫上名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用番茄汁寫「泰泰」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了寫了  所以別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  知道了  那再睡一會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  都滲進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真處理一下的話能弄掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你弄掉的  相對地…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去「Jonny's」？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好  拜託了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人去不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微支持一下我和櫛枝的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的吵死了  我要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}夏日色彩  簡單迷人  讓穿著更上一層的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}6月刊  明日  發售
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛枝…休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勤勞少女偶爾也會休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你只想著自己幸福的懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一會告白一會被告白的你不一樣  我還什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛…眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說讓人害羞的話  發情狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來穿會不會太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的是這個包包啊  包包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是人小腿短啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可從來沒因此給人添麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是包包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個  做模特的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模特？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做川島亞美  聽說是女演員川島安奈的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那樣的女孩會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉亞美  久等了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北…北村…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這不是高須和逢阪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  他們過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…就算這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉扯扯的幹什麼呢  你們關係還是這麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  佑作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想著要介紹一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑作…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是川島亞美  以前住在我家附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所謂的「青梅竹馬」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這邊是高須龍兒和逢阪大河
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅…竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了  剛才在看這個  於是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓別人看見難為情的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服裝和化妝再弄得好一點就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有工作的時候一不經意就鬆懈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…呃  完全沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得這樣  四個人一起聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧  亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人懷念呢  這間店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前經常來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  和家人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  高須也請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫脂奶粉比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣  你是喝純咖啡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  問這麼多幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為佑作也放了  一不在意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又搞砸了  總是會被人說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「其實亞美真是又笨又天然呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…完全沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡吃甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  你真是溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  為什麼要高須來道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了  堅持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我預想的那樣你也離開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你老實回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須覺得亞美怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣  突然把那麼可愛的女孩子帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我緊張得都不知所措了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛這點我承認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還個非常好的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點天然的樣子  還是該說純真呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  先來看一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  亞美美的冰茶喝完了  去幫我拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聾子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來啊  你剛才態度是不是太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對了  讓你的男朋友去幫我拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙好像只要是亞美美說的話什麼都會聽的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美美搶走了也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我一點也不想要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是我男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是怎麼都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  那才是亞美的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又愛撒嬌又任性還粗暴  典型的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能讓人覺得那是個惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  這種什麼都沒有的城市裏\n也就只有那種程度的男人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你身高是多少公分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在才注意到  你的身高是不是太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  原來這種尺寸的衣服也有的賣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  買牛仔褲的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來大河那傢伙  真虧她能冷靜地那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蚊子啊  蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是蒼蠅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了亞美  該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑～作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  逢阪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒了  都煮了2合半了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}1合=180mL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那傢伙的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個性格惡劣的女人  光想起來就讓人肚子餓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「生氣」才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很頭疼哦  北村他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出那種事  我會不會被北村討厭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得那倒不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村也是始終…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭  那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是的  對那個女人色瞇瞇的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底啊  哪會有人自己說自己是「天然」的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正也不會再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我就做回大人  把這份怨恨吞下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起轉來這所學校的川島亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我亞美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給「CanVi」做模特的女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你  神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  請和新的夥伴好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  那麼先安排一下座位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中頭彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這個班級真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得特別顯眼  有點害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  很合適呀  有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  身材也非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快點有和大家一樣的運動衫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美的確很可愛  身材也拔群但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜尋可愛美少女用的小實雷達這次一點都沒反應呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小實…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  為什麼我會在這種什麼都沒的地方摔倒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美很冒失？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有天然成分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是偶爾會被這樣說呢  說「亞美真是天然呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真的不是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我說真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她知道如何掌握人心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我啊  她會轉學過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了的話亞美就不會讓你們看到本性了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  我不討厭亞美的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓大家知道真正的她  喜歡上那樣的她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那樣還是會被討厭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美也會認同的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再讓她繼續偽裝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這種地方有自動售貨機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為第四節課就要開始了  你卻從教室出來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點在意就追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  這傢伙的本性是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在午休之外的時間買飲料是違反校規的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是共犯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢我會付的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就當作為昨天道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學居然是同一個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪同學也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑作什麼都不和我說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  昨天的事  逢阪同學有說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事  都是我的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些時候太笨了  才會惹得逢阪同學生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在很平常的交談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然逢阪同學就說我囂張自大什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是逢阪同學沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是更振作一些的話  也不會變成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣被同性的女孩討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望昨天的事請不要和別人說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  川島想說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以總之先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}註：出自源氏物語第一章第九帖第一段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}「日たけゆきて、儀式もわざとならぬさまにて出で給へり」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}太陽高高地升起  也沒有特別地做什麼準備就出門去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}在这里的「日たけゆきて」是太阳已经高高升起的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}「たけゆきて」的「たけ」也就是「升起向上」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}為什麼會和川島亞美一起在快上課的時候匆匆忙忙回教室  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From實乃梨  To高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學  實乃梨在生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須同學和轉校生好像有些可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見異思遷嗎  是見異思遷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拋棄大河的話  到時我就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教訓你了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  為什麼我會遇上這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須給櫛枝的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是完全不相干的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己說自己天然的人  你會怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到這裏還有不明白的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說高須
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春田說會把田徑部一年級女生的三人一起介紹給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當然會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了也只會讓她們害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是湊數…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌中老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要怎麼做才會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的  弄翻了沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿抹布  你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我在教室等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  為什麼你會在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來  臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是連老師們也要退避三舍的逢阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才去了教員室  老師們全部都說亞美美好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擔心亞美美會不會被逢阪欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像非常讓人討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我和你好好玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙重人格到底能持續到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把你的本性揭露出來很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那樣就太無趣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直監視你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算班級變了  就算畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和跟蹤狂一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人不爽的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣才會沒有朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個來著  高須龍兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一臉不良少年的樣子還對我很著迷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣你就真的變成孤身一人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人覺得可憐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連那個寬大主義者的佑作都討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在家庭餐館對我做的事令他非常難過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是相當地討厭你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完蛋了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川島？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來  讓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～小龍做的炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明剛做好的才最好吃的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去接她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～呆掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河  我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這不是在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈也不開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來叫你吃飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大河  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他討厭…我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人全都說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼沒關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村他全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川島的性格也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家庭餐館為什麼會發生那種事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的謊言也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  北村也不是因為這點事就會討厭別人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你最清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…為什麼我會是小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是奇怪的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為自己有165公分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有個美少女水星戰士一樣的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}註：美少女戰士中水兵水星是水野亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且還因為和北村是青梅竹馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  會在意那種沒辦法的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你不一樣  我可是很纖細的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是吃炸豬排卻沒有豬排醬  這是也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑豬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  布丁呢布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只買醬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰子會遲到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍兒  看下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}川島亞美因為學業要暫時休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是休業的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的學校有讓她停掉工作的價值麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是川島亞美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那些東西  全是甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開家庭聚會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到有趣的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.04,0:23:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過分糾纏不休的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞美美會一下子把我幹掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命名  「笨蛋吉娃娃」

